fm: int countBinarySubstrings(string s) {         int n = s.size(), total = 0, prev = 0, curr = 1;         for (int i = 1; i < n; ++i) {             if (s[i] != s[i - 1]) {                 total += min(prev, curr);                 prev = curr;                 curr = 1;             } else                 ++curr;         }         return total + min(prev, curr);     }

fm: int findShortestSubArray(vector<int> &nums) {         int n = nums.size(), minLen = INT_MAX;         map<int, vector<int>> m;         int size = 0;         for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i) {             m[nums[i]].push_back(i);             if (size < m[nums[i]].size()) {                 size = m[nums[i]].size();             }         }         for (auto iter : m) {             if (iter.second.size() == size)                 minLen = min(minLen, iter.second[iter.second.size() - 1] - iter.second[0] + 1);         }         return minLen;     }
